dialogueTree.title: Lilienne, the Net Picker: ""Huh... haven't seen the RCM around..."
dialogueTree.english: "Huh... haven't seen the RCM around for ages."
dialogueTree.polish: „Hę...? Od wieków nie było tu MOR-u”.

dialogueTree.title: Lilienne, the Net Picker: ""Thought you guys forgot this place..."
dialogueTree.english: "Thought you guys forgot this place even exists."
dialogueTree.polish: „Myślałam, że zapomnieliście, że to miejsce w ogóle istnieje”.
dialogueTree.belarusian: "Я думала, што вы ўжо забыліся, што гэта месца наогул існуе".

dialogueTree.title: Lilienne, the Net Picker: ""It's kinda nice seeing cops around..."
Lilienne, the Net Picker: ""Goddamnit... I *just* bought that..."
Lilienne, the Net Picker: ""I really need to get out there, ca..."
dialogueTree.english: "I really need to get out there, catch something."
dialogueTree.belarusian: "На самай справе мне трэба выйсці ў адкрытае мора і нешта злавіць".

dialogueTree.title: Lilienne, the Net Picker: ""Hey, kids! Oh... never mind.""
Lilienne, the Net Picker: ""The throw-nets just aren't paying..."
dialogueTree.english: "The throw-nets just aren't paying off this time of the year..."
dialogueTree.polish: „O tej porze roku po prostu nie opłaca się zarzucać sieci...”
dialogueTree.belarusian: "У гэты час года проста не мае сэнсу закідваць сеткі..."

dialogueTree.title: Lilienne, the Net Picker: ""It's yellowfin season soon.""
